        <header>Craft (Pharmaceutical) Trained Only</header>
        <text>   This skill allows a character to compound medicinal drugs to aid in recovery from treatable illnesses, and aid in recovering health.
        </text>
        <text><b>Antibacterial/Antiviral</b> These are medicines that help combat disease. An antibacterial/antiviral drug gives a bonus on Fortitude Saves made to resist the effects of a disease. The amount listed is for five doses.
