        <text><b>Special</b></text>
        <text>   A character without a chemistry kit takes a −6 penalty on Craft (Pharmaceutical) checks.</text>
        <text>   A character with 7 ranks in Knowledge (Earth and Life Sciences) can choose Craft (Pharmaceutical) to receive a +2 synergy bonus. If the character chooses Craft (Pharmaceutical), they cannot apply the synergy bonus to any other skill.</text>
